headline: 2 Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stocks to Buy Before They Soar 124% and 136%, According to Certain Wall Street Analysts
summary: The Nasdaq Composite (NASDAQINDEX: ^IXIC) has dropped 8% from the record high in reached in February.  Dan Ives at Wedbush recently set his bull-case target price on Tesla at $650 per share.  Ives expects demand to improve and the Trump administration to fast-track its entrance into the robotaxi market.
